Package grafioschtrader.connector.calendar

Interface ISplitCalendarFeedConnector

All Known Implementing Classes:
InvestingSplitCalendar, YahooSplitCalendar
public interface ISplitCalendarFeedConnector
Interface for split calendar feed connectors that retrieve stock split information from external data sources. Implementations provide split data for specific dates with support for country filtering and connector prioritization.

  • Method Details

    • getCalendarSplitForSingleDay

      Map<String,ISplitCalendarFeedConnector.TickerSecuritysplit> getCalendarSplitForSingleDay(LocalDate forDate, String[] countyCodes) throws Exception
      Retrieves stock split data for all securities on the specified date. Results can be filtered by country codes to limit the scope of data retrieval.
      Parameters:
      forDate - the date for which to retrieve split information
      countyCodes - array of country codes to filter results, or null for all countries
      Returns:
      map of ticker symbols to TickerSecuritysplit objects containing split data
      Throws:
      Exception - if data retrieval fails due to network issues, authentication problems, or data provider errors

    • getPriority

      int getPriority()
      Returns the priority ranking of this split calendar connector. Lower numbers indicate higher priority - connectors with priority 1 are consulted before those with priority 2, etc.
      Returns:
      integer representing the priority of this connector (lower = higher priority)
